title: Updates to Farms
body:
# We are proposing updates to the farm LPs in order to:

1. Continue to reward CAKE-BNB LPs
2. Improve stable coin slippage
3. Improve routing
4. Reduce rewards to low liquidity / low volume farms
5. Add in a farm for a top 10 coin by MCap (LTC)

**The proposed updates are as below:**

| Action   | Farm  LP    | New Weight | Change |  |
|--------|-----------|------------|--------|---|
| Remove  | USDC-BNB  |          0 |     -1 |  
| Remove | DAI-BNB   |          0 |     -1 |   
| New     | DAI-BUSD  |        0.5 |    0.5 |   
| New      | USDC-BUSD |        0.5 |    0.5 |   
| New    | LTC-BNB   |          2 |      2 |   
| Update | YFI-BNB   |          1 |     -1 |   
| Change | YFII-BNB  |        0.5 |   -0.5 |   
| Change | ASR-BNB   |        0.5 |   -0.5 |   
| Change | ATM-BNB   |        0.5 |   -0.5 |   
| Change | OG-BNB    |        0.5 |   -0.5 |   
| Change | PSG-BNB   |        0.5 |   -0.5 |
| Change | JUV-BNB   |        0.5 |   -0.5 | 
| Change | CAKE-BNB  |         40 |     10
